:"<blockquote><blockquote>如果16，7歲既情侶可能會覺得咁做好浪漫<br />\n但係有番咁上下年紀既就會覺得咁做好幼稚<br />\n一個成年人應該大把重要事等住做<br />\n唔會咁得閒咁晒錢咁高調搞個驚喜</blockquote><br />\n調返轉諗 一個成年人為左另一半開心晒少少時間 係一件更浪漫既事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成年 + 做腦細唔係幫人打工 + 有錢 =&gt; 有錢有時間去浪漫<br />\n<br />\n成年 + 幫腦細打工 + 無錢 =&gt; 無錢無時間去浪漫"},{"pid":"2b70c1e4ff120b7996880ac19cfa823929cc46ae","tid":402944,"uid":21260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T05:29:39.000Z","msg":"識佢老鼠"},{"pid":"36bec80603d4356ac34bb017b3a0e3888ac57b85","tid":402944,"uid":60412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"鐘意你咪覺得浪漫lor, 唔鐘意就覺得晒錢晒時間"},{"pid":"4c2b62dd802a665c56fef0144b0a20a9c59e6ad8","tid":402944,"uid":111253,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T05:38:50.000Z","msg":"條仔個樣唔差架喎講真, 佢值得搵過個更好"},{"pid":"286ea4dc2f1b49aa0013a68103edb3fc9fe8db0e","tid":402944,"uid":15353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T05:41:24.000Z","msg":"落花有意隨流水<br />\n流水無情戀落花<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b09b16082f78e30d515cea2408e1c9e97ba015","tid":402944,"uid":3735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"條仔直頭留係台灣溝件大波台妹啦 洗為條咁撚柒既港女做埋呢d野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6cfb5c5a15c842cc69158b4513c5a2e677b33e","tid":402944,"uid":115655,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男嘅痴情女嘅雞</blockquote><br />\n全世界女人都係雞<br />\n港男最撚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b653d1dea520d92cbc0f229c3d176d45cb280536","tid":402944,"uid":86408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"等睇左既人知道你做乜條女唔要你就唔要你 清醒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996647aa19a158904ab90671cebe9aabbc1aee51","tid":402944,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:15:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170916/20154853?_ga=2.55456491.131429822.1505214377-7797648.1439036704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170916%2F20154853%3F_ga%3D2.55456491.131429822.1505214377-7797648.1439036704&d=9emy94v%2FTJBH2%2FQLYpxy8Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=2d3c18f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170916%2F20154853%3F_ga%3D2.55456491.131429822.1505214377-7797648.1439036704&h=e9ad0268\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170916/20154853?_ga=2.55456491.131429822.1505214377-7797648.1439036704</a><br />\n<br />\n香港一名YouTuber上月初上載的短片，近日在內地網上再次被廣傳，名為「搭飛機接女朋友放工」的短片，直擊他從香港飛到台灣，裝成巧遇，接女友放工，送她一個驚喜，短片冧爆無數網民，但原來他倆卻最終結局是分手收場。<br />\n<br />\n這名YouTuber名叫「悶井Moon Cheng」，他拍攝的短片是他從香港機場出發，到達台灣後坐機場捷運到達台北市，之後趕到女友的工作地點，尾隨她下班，最後在扶手電梯上與女友「偶遇」，為女友帶來驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n但有內地媒體近日報道時引述悶井Moon Cheng稱，他與女朋友一起已4年，半個多月前暫時分手，他說:「看來這個行動還是不能解決問題，以後順其自然吧」，《蘋果》記者日前曾接觸他，他表示暫不想再作回應。<br />\n<br />\n不少內地網民都大讚他的行動：「男的很不錯！」「原因很簡單，秀（騷）恩愛！」「女友十分感動！」「異地戀堅持到最後那真的是真愛&hellip;&hellip;」不過，亦有網民分享他的失敗經驗：「我試過從廣州坐高鐵到北京去接女朋友下班，然後突然出現在地鐵口等她的時候，她把我罵到懵了&hellip;&hellip;」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一早估到派帽"},{"pid":"990ee6f4bb4ccb0290925f4889a2ece5c8367ea7","tid":402944,"uid":75131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇完蘋果段片，明哂，原因係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冇錢</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人窮就是原罪<br />\n各位清算吧啦"},